channel.title: Requesting web developer (Paying $)
channel.description:
Our team is in need of a web developer for our project, which can be found here :
http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-server/advertise/429920-draygntiy-old-runescape-back-317-a.html#post3525866
We are looking for someone who can set up the old runescape website (06-07 era) and maybe even some forums, even a normal website would be fine. Contact me on skype / google if you are intrested in helping.
You must be trusted, and must be able to be on actively. If you are interested we can talk about payment and rights ingame/forums
Skype : micahjenkins2
Thank you.
